    "ko": {
      "title": "캡처 UI 탐색",
      "html": "<h3>소개</h3>\n<p><span>캡처 화면을 나가지 않고 캡처 UI에서 캡처 모드 전환, 포인트 편집, 카운트다운 모드 변경 등을 하세요.</span></p>\n<h3>누가 이 기능을 사용할 수 있나요?</h3>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td> </td>\n<td><strong>최고 관리자</strong></td>\n<td><strong>사이트 관리자</strong></td>\n<td><strong>팀 관리자</strong></td>\n<td><strong>촬영 담당자</strong></td>\n<td><strong>협력자</strong></td>\n<td><strong>열람자</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Beamo <span>앱</span> </td>\n<td><strong>✓</strong></td>\n<td><strong>✓</strong></td>\n<td><strong>✓</strong></td>\n<td><strong>✓</strong></td>\n<td>–</td>\n<td>–</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>캡처 UI</h3>\n<p><img src=\"images/v2-capture-ui/img-1.png\" alt=\"_____ui.png\" /></p>\n<h3>UI 설정</h3>\n<p><span>캡처 UI에서 [설정]을 눌러서 설정으로 들어갑니다.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"images/v2-capture-ui/img-2.png\" alt=\"_____ui______.png\" /></p>\n<h4><strong>일반 설정</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">\n<strong>캡처 모드  </strong><span>캡처 모드를 <a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/ko/articles/360003663995\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">자동</a> 혹은 <a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/ko/articles/360003663975\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">수동</a>으로 바꿀 수 있습니다.</span><span><br></span>\n</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">\n<strong>카운트다운  </strong><span><a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/ko/articles/360003663995\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">자동</a> 모드의 타이머를 변경합니다.</span><span><br></span>\n</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">\n<strong>그리드 　</strong><span>도면의 그리드(격자판)를 켜거나 끕니다.</span><span><br></span>\n</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">\n<span>리모컨</span><strong>　</strong><span><a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/ko/articles/360003623736\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BLE 리모컨</a>을 켜거나 끕니다.</span><span><br></span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4><strong>360도 카메라 정보</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">\n<span>연결된 카메라 모델을 확인합니다.</span><span><br></span>\n</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">\n<span>배터리 충전 정도를 확인합니다.</span><span><br></span>\n</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><span><a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/ko/articles/4427785033359\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">360° 카메라 설정</a>을 변경합니다.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><strong>알림</strong></h4>\n<ul data-indent-level=\"1\">\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"442\"><strong>경보　</strong><span><a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/ko/articles/360003663995\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">자동 캡처</a> 모드에서 카운트다운 알람을 켜거나 끕니다.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"497\"><strong>진동 </strong><span>캡쳐 가능한 두 지점 간 허용 범위(5-10미터)를 벗어나면 알립니다.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>"
    },
    "ja": {
      "title": "キャプチャ画面の説明",
      "html": "<h3>イントロダクション</h3>\n<p>キャプチャー画面では、キャプチャーモードの切り替え、ポイントの編集、カウントダウンモードの変更などを行うことができます。</p>\n<h3>本機能対象ユーザー</h3>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td> </td>\n<td>\n<p><span><strong>スーパー アドミン</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span><strong>サイト マネージャー</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span><strong>チーム </strong><strong>アドミン</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span><strong>サーベイヤー</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span><strong>コラボレーター</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span><strong>ビューアー</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Beamo アプリ使用</td>\n<td>\n<p><span><strong>✓</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span><strong>✓</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span><strong>✓</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span><strong>✓</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>–</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>–</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>キャプチャ画面</h3>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img src=\"images/v2-capture-ui/img-3.png\" alt=\"________.png\" /></p>\n<h3>キャプチャ設定画面</h3>\n<h4>\n<img src=\"images/v2-capture-ui/img-4.png\" alt=\"Setting_.png\" /><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">設定</strong>\n</h4>\n<ul data-indent-level=\"1\">\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"63\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">キャプチャモード　</strong><a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/ja/articles/360003663975\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">手動モード</a>と<a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/ja/articles/360003663995\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">自動モード</a>を切り替えます。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"98\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">カウントダウン　</strong>自動モードのタイマーを設定します。 </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"132\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">グリッドモード　</strong>フロアプラン上のグリッドの<strong>オン・オフ</strong>を設定します。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"168\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">リモコン　</strong><a title=\"https://3iai.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/IN/pages/123339739\" href=\"https://3iai.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/IN/pages/123339739\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">BLE</strong>リモコン</a>の接続の<strong>オン・オフ</strong>を設定します。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"３６０度カメラ情報\" data-renderer-start-pos=\"202\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">３６０°カメラ情報</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"215\">接続中の<strong>360°カメラの機種</strong>を確認します。</li>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"215\">360°カメラの<strong>使用済みメモリ量</strong>を確認します。</li>\n<li data-renderer-start-pos=\"215\">\n<strong><a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/ja/articles/4427785033359\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">360°カメラを設定を実施します</a></strong>。</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"通知\" data-renderer-start-pos=\"271\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">通知</strong></h4>\n<ul data-indent-level=\"1\">\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"277\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">振動　</strong>設定間隔を超えたことを警告する振動の<strong>オン・オフ</strong>を設定します。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"313\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">アラーム</strong>　カウントダウンの電子音の<strong>オン・オフ</strong>を設定します<strong>。</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>"
    },
    "en": {
      "title": "Navigating the Capture UI",
      "html": "<h3>Introduction</h3>\n<p>In the capture UI, switch from capture mode, edit points, change the countdown mode, etc., without leaving the capture screen.</p>\n<h3>Who can use this feature? </h3>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td> </td>\n<td>\n<strong>Super A</strong><strong>dmin</strong>\n</td>\n<td><strong>Site Manager</strong></td>\n<td><strong>Team Admin</strong></td>\n<td><strong>Surveyor</strong></td>\n<td><strong>Collaborator</strong></td>\n<td><strong>Viewer</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Beamo App </td>\n<td><strong>✓</strong></td>\n<td><strong>✓</strong></td>\n<td><strong>✓</strong></td>\n<td><strong>✓</strong></td>\n<td>–</td>\n<td>–</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>Capture UI</h3>\n<p><img src=\"images/v2-capture-ui/img-5.png\" alt=\"capture_UI.png\" /></p>\n<h3>Settings UI</h3>\n<p>Go to the settings by tapping <strong>[Settings]</strong> in the capture UI.</p>\n<p><img src=\"images/v2-capture-ui/img-6.png\" alt=\"Setting_.png\" /></p>\n<h4><strong>General Settings</strong></h4>\n<ul data-indent-level=\"1\">\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"108\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Capture Mode: </strong>Switch between <a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/en-us/articles/360003663995\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">auto</a>/<a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/en-us/articles/360003663975\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">manual capture mode.</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"160\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Countdown: </strong>Change the timer for <a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/en-us/articles/360003663995\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">auto-capture mode.</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"214\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Grid: </strong><span>Switch ON/OFF to show or not show the grid on the floor plan. </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"266\"><strong>Remote Control: <span>Switch ON/OFF to connect or disable <a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/en-us/articles/360003623736\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">the BLE remote control</a>.</span></strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"360-degree-camera-information\" data-renderer-start-pos=\"326\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">360<span>°</span> camera information</strong></h4>\n<ul data-indent-level=\"1\">\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"359\">Check the connected camera model.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"395\">Check the charged battery. </p>\n</li>\n<li>Change the <a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/en-us/articles/4427785033359\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">360<span>°</span> camera settings</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4><strong>Notifications</strong></h4>\n<ul data-indent-level=\"1\">\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"442\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Alarm: <span>Switch ON/OFF to enable or disable the alarm for the countdown in</span></strong> <a href=\"https://support.beamo.ai/hc/en-us/articles/360003663995\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">auto-capture mode.</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"497\"><strong data-renderer-mark=\"true\">Vibration: <span>Switch ON/OFF to enable or disable notifications when you have exceeded the set distance.</span></strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>"
    }
  }
}
